            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-vmark="0c4d">IT之家 4 月 15 日消息，华为终端 BG 首席执行官何刚今日再次预告了 Pura X Max 横向阔折叠新机。据介绍，<strong>华为 Pura X Max 将支持 AI 眼动翻页、横屏双翻页等功能</strong>，同时阅读软件还支持 AI 动态画面生成。</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="5ad8"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/1f7ae69b-ebdf-4f63-bee1-a6cb8d4e8e60.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" data-mpos="2,0" data-live="https://qimg.ithome.com/newfiles/2026/4/a264b2b8-91e9-42b4-9fbc-b7e147afedf0.mp4" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d135ea7e8a483b3343904dd8c2244ee3bf1fd04beb778a3f53d09ccc51a16d95e588112c15b8fe3a39" data-vmark="08a3" class="no-alt-img"></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="dd8d"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/83d0c00a-24ef-4e7d-b000-1c352a3b0d6d.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" data-mpos="0,2" data-live="https://qimg.ithome.com/newfiles/2026/4/3b8216f2-3e48-4fa1-b4c9-48d1a0e759b0.mp4" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d1ab54fdba0074072590c9bfd1632be85eab28c5fb27500f64b87a6a2db407b692868adb8ddbdb0628" data-vmark="e1af" class="no-alt-img"></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="9f68"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/35a9763f-29d0-457a-b3e2-8fa79eba3b45.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" data-mpos="2,0" data-live="https://qimg.ithome.com/newfiles/2026/4/ae7f6a77-07a8-40d8-a775-d9f448026e35.mp4" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d1f083e4b548e38fcf850ae04e4237a28fd044bbdee36bab1a21a3d14f13e54ae010d0a14aa2616266" data-vmark="8308" class="no-alt-img"></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="1c3f"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/e7a448ca-103b-4640-9c45-014e7b1d2b40.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" data-mpos="0,2" data-live="https://qimg.ithome.com/newfiles/2026/4/55d36b32-5d43-4e30-bd4c-43cf2ece03da.mp4" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d159826d64e156b1339a8640992c7f216c154ff11d824dca782e3a4302742f0ea8f1beecf10c6b1e06" data-vmark="3730" class="no-alt-img"></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="0c4b"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/a0688311-0514-4175-b98b-7baa6db0d0ed.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1080" h="1440" data-mpos="0,2" data-live="https://qimg.ithome.com/newfiles/2026/4/eaa3ff02-465e-459b-b27a-09bedd659657.mp4"  data-vmark="7710" class="no-alt-img"></p><p data-vmark="17ed">IT之家注意到，华为 Pura X Max 已正式亮相，新机是行业首款横向阔折叠手机，定档 4 月 20 日发布。官网显示，新机可选幻夜黑、橄榄金等 5 款配色，同时拥有典藏版可选。</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="cb20"><a class="ithome_super_player" href="https://weibo.com/1839167003/QAzM303cE"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/5a5384dc-7986-4843-9a2f-b61ab9d09b0f.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="810"></a></p><p class="j_iframe_show ithome-content-placeholder" style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="1692"><iframe src="https://img.ithome.com/app/calendar/event_card.html?id=3991" frameborder="no"></iframe></p>]]></content:encoded>
